FBIS3-52536 "drnes004dd_94011" FBIS-NES-94-004 Document Type:Daily Report 6 Jan 1994 Palestinian Affairs PLO Leadership Agrees to Consultative Body TA0501182594 Jerusalem Israel Television Channel 1 Network in Arabic 1700 GMT 5 Jan 94 TA0501182594 Jerusalem Israel Television Channel 1 Network in Arabic 1700 GMT 5 Jan 94 Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] Palestinian sources in Tunis have informed our correspondent Yoni Ben-Menahem that the delegation of Palestinian figures, headed by Dr. Haydar 'Abd-al-Shafi, will meet tonight with PLO Executive Committee members in order to sum up the talks on PLO internal reforms. The figures have expressed their satisfaction with the results of the meetings that have taken place so far. They said that the PLO leadership has agreed, in principle, to set up a special consultative body to support the Executive Committee. A statement on the results of these talks is expected to be issued tomorrow.
